        <section>
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>
                Haven Hotel & Corporate Suites is a thoughtfully designed boutique hotel in Gurugram, created for guests who value comfort, quality, and a seamless stay experience. Located in Sector 31, Gurugram, the hotel enjoys excellent connectivity to major business hubs, leisure destinations, hospitals, and metro access.
                With over 6+ years of hands-on experience in hotel and cafe operations, Haven Hotel has built a reputation for reliable service and consistent quality. Over the years, we have proudly hosted more than 1,00,000 guests and prepared over 15,00,000 dishes, reflecting our strong focus on hospitality excellence and guest satisfaction.
                Haven Hotel is part of the Be Raw hospitality group, known for its commitment to clean spaces, quality food, and guest-first service. Our in-house Be Raw Cafe makes us a preferred hotel with cafe in Gurugram for stays, dining, and small celebrations.
                We welcome corporate travelers, leisure guests, couples, families, friends, production houses, shooting crews, and long-stay professionals. What sets Haven Hotel apart is our attention to cleanliness, comfort, and personalized care, ensuring every guest feels relaxed and well looked after.
                The hotel is conveniently located near key landmarks including HUDA City Centre Metro Station, Sector 29 Market and Leisure Hub, Cyber City, Golf Course Road, and NH-48 (Delhi–Jaipur Highway). We are also well-connected to major offices, hospitals, and popular production shoot locations, making Haven Hotel an ideal choice for both short and extended stays in Gurugram.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h1>Mission</h1>
            <p>
                To deliver a boutique hospitality experience built on comfort, quality service, and good food, ensuring every guest enjoys a relaxed and memorable stay.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h1>Vision</h1>
            <p>
                To be a preferred boutique hotel in Gurugram, recognized for comfortable stays, trusted dining at Be Raw Cafe, and personalized experiences for business and leisure travelers alike.
            </p>
        </section>
    </section>
